commitResults.messageTitle: Add an assert to sanity check the fromStorageStr() functions
commitResults.messageBody:
These assertions help to ensure that the correct version of the
fromStorageStr() function is being called when parsing a storage
String.

Asserting that the first letter of the string corresponds to the
class of the fromStorageStr() being called helps to ensure this.
